data.description: Looking for a home on acreage with 360 views on a paved road? Well, look no more, this home has it all. This custom-built 2312 sq ft. home is on 37.48 acres of completely usable land. The house has 3 large bedroom and 2 bathrooms. The kitchen has solid oak cabinets, a custom-made bar and more. The laundry room is off the kitchen and has an outside door. The dining area and living room have a spiral staircase leading to the ''family room'' that has windows all the way around for spectating mountains by day and star gazing by night! The outside has approx. 1 acre that is fully fenced with a small grove of fruit trees (pecan, peach, apple, fig) and a lovely sitting area to watch the mountains and nature like seeing the rare Calliope Hummingbird and 55 other species as well. Call today!
